name: 夜蘭 - Yelan LORA. / Genshin Impact - 原神.
description:
N°18 Release, 夜蘭 - Yelan from Genshin Impact - 原神.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Character's Request from My Poll & I wanted to create My Lora of Yelan like i did for Kuki Shinobu.

One of the Big Dataset i sorted many different Angles & Positions, This Lora is trained on 419+ Images with Good quality, I sorted everything manually, Only picked the best possible. (SFW + NFSW)

Honestly i think the Quality Output is Insane, specially when you Edit & Combine with Added Detail Lora.

AnimeFullFinalPrunedFP16 used, so he work with the majority of Anime Model, you can see in examples images.

This Lora of Yelan Have: Official Default Skin + Also Other Clothes that don't exist (Like Yelan Leotard).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: YelanV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples image.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Work perfectly at Weight 1, Best result: 0.7-1 (You can Even go to 1.4 Weight i tested it it's work ahah, But i recommend 1 for Official Default Skin).

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.description:
For Flexibility for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

I pruned Green eyes Prompt so normally you don't have to put it in prompt, but if it's not appear just force it with: ((Green Eyes) prompt.

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Prompt.
